name: Ats - FlyExp
tagline: Simple And Fast File Explorer For Android
body:
### Welcome to Ats-FlyExp - The All New File Explorer For Android .
Ats-FlyExp is an Open Source File Explorer which having inspirations from CM Filemanager.
To Clone this to Your github:-  

```
$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

If you're using the GitHub for Mac, simply sync your repository and you'll see the new branch.
